Class DmwWrapper

Direct Known Subclasses:
ActionTriggerInfoDMW, ClientCountFilterDMW, DmgConfigDMW, DMPMessageDMW, DmwNamedObjectWrapper, NameContainerTestDMW, TestAbstractExtendedDMW, TestAbstractFixedDMW, TestBasicObjectFixedDMW
public abstract class DmwWrapper
extends DmcContainer

The DmwWrapper class provides a common base for Dark Matter Wrapper classes in a Full Java Environment and provides basic functionality beyond what's defined for a DmcContainer.
